{"about_the_game":"Ready to die? Experience the newest brutal action game from Team NINJA and Koei Tecmo Games. In the age of samurai, a lone traveler lands on the shores of Japan. He must fight his way through the vicious warriors and supernatural Yokai that infest the land in order to find that which he seeks.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/NiohCE_01.jpg?t=1737983043\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/NiohCE_02.jpg?t=1737983043\" /><br><br> The Complete Edition contains the full game, as well as the three expansions with additional story chapters: Dragon of the North, Defiant Honor, and Bloodshed's End.<br><br>Dragon of the North<br>This expansion opens up the Tohoku region, where the &quot;one-eyed dragon&quot; Date Masamune is secretly gathering spirit stones.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/DLC01_KeyArt.jpg?t=1737983043\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/DLC01_SS.jpg?t=1737983043\" /><br><br>Defiant Honor<br>Fight your way through the Siege of Osaka's winter campaign as you follow the story of one of Japan's greatest generals from the Warring States period, the brave Sanada Yukimura.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/DLC02_KeyArt.jpg?t=1737983043\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/DLC02_SS.jpg?t=1737983043\" /><br><br>Bloodshed's End<br>Join the summer campaign of the Siege of Osaka as the Warring States period draws to a close in this, the final chapter of William's tale.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/DLC03_KeyArt.jpg?t=1737983043\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/DLC03_SS.jpg?t=1737983043\" /><br><br>Steam Exclusive Bonus<br>Enjoy wearing the &quot;Dharmachakra Kabuto,&quot; a helmet exclusive to the Steam version of Nioh! You can claim yours by selecting &quot;Boons&quot; from a shrine.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/485510/extras/NiohCE_bonus.jpg?t=1737983043\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"You Are Nioh","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/485510/e089fd0d40e621f1aece46d73474024b4164624a.jpg"},{"name":"A Long Journey Begins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/485510/e7431caee596de01704beaa3019d5b19b579c6c7.jpg"},{"name":"They Call Him Anjin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/485510/6a7957fc394d7fbb16c6199a2f302c6730e93906.jpg"},{"name":"An Agreement Forged","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/485510/380fb2375de0b5bf4c3a98e56c3053c09bf963b7.jpg"},{"name":"Wandering Spirit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/485510/105a30f819eb6fffcd17074102f719bfce8cbb7f.jpg"},{"name":"A Question of Intentions","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/485510/e0ec01fda348daf063ecbed14aa4d755f7f6ff1c.jpg"},{"name":"Onward to a Decisive Battle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/485510/77bdfc674a579e4a741a9403dec13cc9de182031.jpg"},{"name":"The Battle Ends","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/485510/511c7366985b313cf9ee1d5cb332cbb75008f6ba.jpg"},{"name":"A True Samurai","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/485510/13c4627ef20223047c8c5e2f39754